# Scripts

Shell scripts for project setup, bootstrap, and maintenance.

## Main Scripts

| Script                    | Purpose                                                 |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| `install/install-all.zsh` | Install ALL development prerequisites (Linux/macOS/WSL) |
| `install/install-all.ps1` | Install ALL prerequisites (Windows PowerShell)          |
| `bootstrap.zsh`           | Full project bootstrap (deps, hooks, env)               |
| `health-check.zsh`        | Verify all services are healthy                         |
| `seed-database.zsh`       | Seed database with development data                     |
{%- if use_ai %}
| `setup-ai.zsh`            | Validate AI deps, init FAISS/KG/RAG dirs                |
{%- endif %}

## Individual Installers

Individual installers under `install/`, called by `install-all.zsh`:

**Always installed:**

| Script                   | Tool                                |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| `install-git.zsh`        | Git with recommended config         |
| `install-zsh.zsh`        | Zsh with Oh My Zsh                  |
| `install-python.zsh`     | Python via uv                       |
| `install-node.zsh`       | Node.js via fnm + pnpm via corepack |
| `install-container.zsh`  | Docker or Podman                    |
| `install-task.zsh`       | go-task CLI                         |
| `install-vscode.zsh`     | VS Code with extensions             |
| `install-linters.zsh`    | hadolint, shellcheck, yamllint      |

**Conditional:**

| Script                        | Tool                                | Condition                       |
| ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
{%- if use_devcontainer %}
| `setup-devcontainer.zsh`      | @devcontainers/cli                  | `use_devcontainer`              |
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_caddy %}
| `install-caddy.zsh`           | Caddy reverse proxy                 | `use_caddy`                     |
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_redis %}
| `install-redis.zsh`           | Redis server                        | `use_redis`                     |
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_faiss %}
| `install-faiss.zsh`           | FAISS vector store                  | `use_faiss`                     |
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_knowledge_graph and knowledge_graph_backend == 'neo4j' %}
| `install-neo4j.zsh`           | Neo4j graph database                | `use_knowledge_graph` + `neo4j` |
{%- endif %}
{%- if cloud_provider != 'none' %}
| `install-cloud-cli.zsh`       | Azure CLI + Bicep                   | `cloud_provider != "none"`      |
{%- endif %}
{%- if with_opencode %}
| `install-opencode.zsh`        | OpenCode CLI                        | `with_opencode`                 |
| `install-opencode-ecosystem.zsh` | GSD, OAC, plugins               | `with_opencode`                 |
{%- endif %}

**Windows-only (called by `install-all.ps1`):**

| Script               | Tool                                |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| `install-vscode.ps1` | VS Code with extensions (Windows)   |
| `install-wsl2.ps1`   | WSL2 with Ubuntu                    |

## Quick Start

```bash
zsh scripts/install/install-all.zsh
zsh scripts/bootstrap.zsh
```
